### Commands Implemented

```
harness init                     # Create .harness/harness.db
harness db status                # Show DB info

harness task add "Title"         # Create task
harness task list [--status=X]   # List tasks (paginated)
harness task search "query"      # FTS5 search
harness task get <id>            # Get single task
harness task update <id> ...     # Update fields
harness task delete <id>         # Delete task
harness task reorder <id> --after=<id>

harness step add <task_id> "desc"
harness step list <task_id>
harness step complete <id>
harness step uncomplete <id>
harness step toggle <id>
harness step delete <id>

harness session start [--summary=X]
harness session end [--summary=X]
harness session current
harness session list
harness session get <id>

harness progress add "content" [--session=X]
harness progress list [--session=X]
harness progress search "query"

harness status                   # Project summary
```

